<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="215" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="0.[136,1452,1200,1729]" pageId="0" pageNumber="215">
<emphasis box="[136,229,1201,1224]" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="215">Notes:—</emphasis>
<location LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:411D87E67F7DCD65FF638915FBC4C7A6:CC6B602B7F7DCD65FF0E8ECAFF67C5AF" box="[229,251,1201,1224]" country="Mexico" county="Therefore" municipality="However" name="In" pageId="0" pageNumber="215" stateProvince="Veracruz de Ignacio de la Llave">In</location>
the protologue of 
<taxonomicName box="[450,584,1201,1225]" class="Liliopsida" family="Poaceae" genus="Arundinella" kingdom="Plantae" order="Poales" pageId="0" pageNumber="215" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="deppeana">
<emphasis box="[450,584,1201,1225]" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="215">A. deppeana</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Steudel, E. G." box="[599,749,1200,1225]" pageId="0" pageNumber="215" refId="ref1150" refString="Steudel, E. G. (1855 [1854]) Synopsis Plantarum Glumacearum. Pars I. Gramineae. J. B. Metzler, Stuttgart, 475 pp. https: // doi. org / 10.5962 / bhl. title. 471" type="book" year="1855">Steudel, 1855</bibRefCitation>
(1854)), the locality of 
<location LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:411D87E67F7DCD65FF638915FBC4C7A6:CC6B602B7F7DCD65FC0E8ECAFBD9C5AE" box="[997,1093,1201,1225]" country="Mexico" county="Therefore" municipality="However" name="Misantla" pageId="0" pageNumber="215" stateProvince="Veracruz de Ignacio de la Llave">Misantla</location>
, 
<collectingRegion box="[1103,1201,1201,1224]" country="Mexico" name="Veracruz de Ignacio de la Llave" pageId="0" pageNumber="215">Veracruz</collectingRegion>
, 
<collectingCountry box="[1212,1296,1201,1225]" name="Mexico" pageId="0" pageNumber="215">Mexico</collectingCountry>
, is mentioned, and no other information, such as collector or herbarium where it was deposited, is indicated. 
<location LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:411D87E67F7DCD65FF638915FBC4C7A6:CC6B602B7F7DCD65FB898EAEFB2FC58A" box="[1122,1203,1237,1261]" country="Mexico" county="Therefore" municipality="However" name="Various" pageId="0" pageNumber="215" stateProvince="Veracruz de Ignacio de la Llave">Various</location>
authors have attributed the type to 
<location LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:411D87E67F7DCD65FF638915FBC4C7A6:CC6B602B7F7DCD65FF168E82FE29C477" box="[253,437,1273,1297]" country="Mexico" county="Therefore" municipality="However" name="Ferdinand Deppe" pageId="0" pageNumber="215" stateProvince="Veracruz de Ignacio de la Llave">Ferdinand Deppe</location>
(e.g., 
<bibRefCitation author="Davidse, G." box="[503,660,1273,1297]" pageId="0" pageNumber="215" pagination="1 - 662" refId="ref796" refString="Davidse, G. (2003) Arundinella. In: Zuloaga, F. O., Morrone, O., Davidse, G., Filgueiras, T. S., Peterson, P. M, Soreng, R. J. &amp; Judziewicz, E. J. (Eds.) Catalogue of New World Grasses (Poaceae): III. Subfamilies Panicoideae, Aristidoideae, Arundinoideae and Danthonioideae. Contributions from the United States National Herbarium 46: 1 - 662." type="journal article" year="2003">Davidse, 2003</bibRefCitation>
), a 
<location LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:411D87E67F7DCD65FF638915FBC4C7A6:CC6B602B7F7DCD65FD538E82FC92C476" box="[696,782,1273,1297]" country="Mexico" county="Therefore" municipality="However" name="German" pageId="0" pageNumber="215" stateProvince="Veracruz de Ignacio de la Llave">German</location>
naturalist who collected plants in various locations in 
<collectingRegion box="[1357,1452,1273,1296]" country="Mexico" name="Veracruz de Ignacio de la Llave" pageId="0" pageNumber="215">Veracruz</collectingRegion>
between 1828 and 1829, together with 
<location LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:411D87E67F7DCD65FF638915FBC4C7A6:CC6B602B7F7DCD65FDD18F66FCDDC452" box="[570,833,1309,1333]" country="Mexico" county="Therefore" municipality="However" name="Christian Julius Schiede" pageId="0" pageNumber="215" stateProvince="Veracruz de Ignacio de la Llave">Christian Julius Schiede</location>
(Streseman, 1954). 
<location LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:411D87E67F7DCD65FF638915FBC4C7A6:CC6B602B7F7DCD65FBC98F66FBDBC452" box="[1058,1095,1309,1333]" country="Mexico" county="Therefore" municipality="However" name="His" pageId="0" pageNumber="215" stateProvince="Veracruz de Ignacio de la Llave">His</location>
collections were sold to several 
<location LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:411D87E67F7DCD65FF638915FBC4C7A6:CC6B602B7F7DCD65FF638F3AFF72C43F" box="[136,238,1345,1368]" country="Mexico" county="Therefore" municipality="However" name="European" pageId="0" pageNumber="215" stateProvince="Veracruz de Ignacio de la Llave">European</location>
herbaria after 1829. 
<bibRefCitation author="Sanchez-Ken, J. G." box="[462,681,1345,1369]" pageId="0" pageNumber="215" refId="ref972" refString="Sanchez-Ken, J. G. (2020) Familia Gramineae. Subfamilia Panicoideae I. In: Rzedowski, J. &amp; Hernandez Ledesma, P. (Eds.) Flora del Bajio y de Regiones Adyacentes. Vol. 216. Instituto de Ecologia, A. C., Patzcuaro, 24 pp." type="book" year="2020">Sánchez-Ken (2020)</bibRefCitation>
mentions that there is a specimen in the 
<location LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:411D87E67F7DCD65FF638915FBC4C7A6:CC6B602B7F7DCD65FBB58F3AFB0FC43E" box="[1118,1171,1345,1369]" country="Mexico" county="Therefore" municipality="However" name="Paris" pageId="0" pageNumber="215" stateProvince="Veracruz de Ignacio de la Llave">Paris</location>
herbarium (P-01863650!) that was collected in 
<location LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:411D87E67F7DCD65FF638915FBC4C7A6:CC6B602B7F7DCD65FE8D8F1EFE5FC41A" box="[358,451,1381,1405]" country="Mexico" county="Therefore" municipality="However" name="Misantla" pageId="0" pageNumber="215" stateProvince="Veracruz de Ignacio de la Llave">Misantla</location>
by Schiede. This author also indicates that it is likely this specimen is the type of 
<emphasis box="[1312,1451,1381,1405]" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="215">
<taxonomicName box="[1312,1447,1381,1405]" class="Liliopsida" family="Poaceae" genus="Arundinella" kingdom="Plantae" order="Poales" pageId="0" pageNumber="215" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="deppeana">A. deppeana</taxonomicName>
,
</emphasis>
where for reasons unbeknownst, 
<location LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:411D87E67F7DCD65FF638915FBC4C7A6:CC6B602B7F7DCD65FE038FF2FDA3C4C6" box="[488,575,1417,1441]" country="Mexico" county="Therefore" municipality="However" name="Deppe's" pageId="0" pageNumber="215" stateProvince="Veracruz de Ignacio de la Llave">Deppe’s</location>
name was not included on the label. 
<collectingMunicipality box="[972,1071,1417,1440]" pageId="0" pageNumber="215">However</collectingMunicipality>
, at this moment there is not enough evidence to know unequivocally if the mentioned specimen is type material. 
<collectingCounty box="[948,1056,1453,1477]" pageId="0" pageNumber="215">Therefore</collectingCounty>
, a 
<typeStatus box="[1084,1182,1453,1477]" pageId="0" pageNumber="215">lectotype</typeStatus>
of the name 
<taxonomicName box="[1319,1452,1453,1477]" class="Liliopsida" family="Poaceae" genus="Arundinella" kingdom="Plantae" order="Poales" pageId="0" pageNumber="215" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="deppeana">
<emphasis box="[1319,1452,1453,1477]" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="215">A. deppeana</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is not designated herein.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="0.[136,1452,1200,1729]" pageId="0" pageNumber="215">
Three synonyms are recognized for 
<taxonomicName box="[580,715,1525,1549]" class="Liliopsida" family="Poaceae" genus="Arundinella" kingdom="Plantae" order="Poales" pageId="0" pageNumber="215" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="deppeana">
<emphasis box="[580,715,1525,1549]" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="215">A. deppeana</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
: 
<taxonomicName box="[730,847,1525,1549]" class="Liliopsida" family="Poaceae" genus="Arundinella" kingdom="Plantae" order="Poales" pageId="0" pageNumber="215" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="auletica">
<emphasis box="[730,847,1525,1549]" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="215">A. auletica</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName box="[862,976,1525,1549]" class="Liliopsida" family="Poaceae" genus="Arundinella" kingdom="Plantae" order="Poales" pageId="0" pageNumber="215" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="latifolia">
<emphasis box="[862,976,1525,1549]" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="215">A. latifolia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName box="[1031,1143,1525,1549]" class="Liliopsida" family="Poaceae" genus="Arundinella" kingdom="Plantae" order="Poales" pageId="0" pageNumber="215" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="robusta">
<emphasis box="[1031,1143,1525,1549]" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="215">A. robusta</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. All of them were described by the French botanist Eugène Fournier in the second volume of Mexicanas Plantas (1886), dedicated to the grasses. For 
<taxonomicName box="[136,253,1597,1621]" class="Liliopsida" family="Poaceae" genus="Arundinella" kingdom="Plantae" order="Poales" pageId="0" pageNumber="215" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="auletica">
<emphasis box="[136,253,1597,1621]" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="215">A. auletica</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<specimenCount box="[260,431,1597,1621]" pageId="0" pageNumber="215" type="generic" typeStatus="syntypes">eleven syntypes</specimenCount>
are cited, from which the specimen 
<emphasis box="[826,974,1596,1621]" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="215">Galeotti 5679</emphasis>
at K is chosen as 
<typeStatus box="[1173,1271,1597,1621]" pageId="0" pageNumber="215">lectotype</typeStatus>
because it is the most complete. For 
<taxonomicName box="[351,463,1633,1657]" class="Liliopsida" family="Poaceae" genus="Arundinella" kingdom="Plantae" order="Poales" pageId="0" pageNumber="215" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="robusta">
<emphasis box="[351,463,1633,1657]" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="215">A. robusta</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<specimenCount box="[469,601,1633,1657]" pageId="0" pageNumber="215" type="generic" typeStatus="syntypes">six syntypes</specimenCount>
are cited, from which only the series of 
<emphasis box="[1038,1203,1632,1656]" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="215">Bourgeau 1660</emphasis>
could be localized and the specimen at MPU is chosen as 
<typeStatus box="[508,609,1669,1693]" pageId="0" pageNumber="215">lectotype</typeStatus>
. Finally, for 
<taxonomicName box="[745,859,1669,1693]" class="Liliopsida" family="Poaceae" genus="Arundinella" kingdom="Plantae" order="Poales" pageId="0" pageNumber="215" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="latifolia">
<emphasis box="[745,859,1669,1693]" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="215">A. latifolia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, only the specimen 
<emphasis box="[1074,1276,1668,1693]" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="215">Bourgeau 1660 bis</emphasis>
is cited, and the herbarium where it was deposited is not indicated. The specimen at P is chosen as lectoype.
</paragraph>
